Evolution
Pokedex

Egg group - WATER 3

This iguana has scales made of hardened minerals that give superb defense against non-physical attacks. It is said that these colorful minerals are harder than diamonds.
Aquana's mineral scales were weathered by rough sandstorms to evolve into this armored iguana. Its minerals are imbued with magical gifts.
